cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NA, cs.SI 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically in the area of texture analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves mathematical concepts such as fractal dimension and filtering, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The use of CNN-based architecture for implementation suggests the possibility of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
